Carol Smillie, who is best known for hosting Changing Rooms, touched down in New York City where she visited son, Robbie Knight. The 60-year-old wowed fans as she sported a blue floral dress with a plunging neckline as she enjoyed the warm weather and tourist sights in Manhatten. She looked radiant as she donned a casual hairstyle and a big smile. The ex-telly host wrote as the caption: “Days 2&3 in NYC being tourists,” while she and her son clutched onto bikes. She was swiftly inundated with messages from fans who gushed over Carol and her son Robbie in the candid holiday snaps.